INSERT INTO guest_reviews (source, reviewer_name, reviewer_country, rating, title, content, review_date, room_number, sentiment, tags, has_reply, reply_text, reply_date) VALUES
('booking', 'James Wilson', 'Australia', 4, NULL, 'Great apartment, fantastic location. Bed was a bit firm for my liking but overall excellent stay.', '2025-12-08', 'C-0718', 'positive', '["location", "comfort"]', true, 'Thank you James! We appreciate your feedback and will look into softer mattress options.', '2025-12-10'),
('booking', 'Olga Petrova', 'Russia', 5, NULL, 'Прекрасный вид на море! Квартира чистая и современная. Очень довольны отдыхом.', '2025-12-11', 'B-1405', 'positive', '["view", "cleanliness"]', false, NULL, NULL),
('booking', 'Carlos Rodriguez', 'Spain', 5, NULL, 'Excelente ubicación y apartamento muy limpio. El personal fue muy amable. Volveremos seguro!', '2025-12-12', 'A-1105', 'positive', '["location", "cleanliness", "service"]', true, 'Muchas gracias Carlos! Esperamos verle pronto de nuevo!', '2025-12-14'),
('airbnb', 'Sarah Johnson', 'Canada', 5, 'Amazing Batumi Experience', 'This place is absolutely stunning! The views are incredible and the apartment is beautifully decorated. Highly recommend!', '2025-12-11', 'A-1802', 'positive', '["view", "design", "experience"]', true, 'Thank you Sarah! We are so happy you loved your stay. Welcome back anytime!', '2025-12-13'),
('airbnb', 'Michael Brown', 'USA', 5, 'Perfect for remote work', 'Fast WiFi, comfortable workspace, and amazing sea views. Perfect for digital nomads!', '2025-12-09', 'B-0912', 'positive', '["wifi", "workspace", "view"]', false, NULL, NULL),
('expedia', 'David Chen', 'Singapore', 4, NULL, 'Good value for money. Clean apartment with nice views. Check-in was smooth.', '2025-12-06', 'C-1102', 'positive', '["value", "cleanliness", "view"]', false, NULL, NULL),
('tripadvisor', 'Emma Thompson', 'UK', 5, 'Exceeded expectations', 'We stayed for a week and loved every minute. The apartment was immaculate and the location could not be better.', '2025-12-04', 'A-1506', 'positive', '["cleanliness", "location", "value"]', true, 'Dear Emma, thank you for your wonderful review! We hope to welcome you back soon!', '2025-12-07'),
('facebook', 'Natalia Kozlova', 'Belarus', 5, NULL, 'Отличное место! Рекомендую всем! Очень чисто, красивый вид, отзывчивый персонал.', '2025-12-14', 'A-0705', 'positive', '["cleanliness", "view", "service"]', true, 'Спасибо большое, Наталья! Ждем вас снова!', '2025-12-15'),
('google', 'Ivan Kozlov', 'Russia', 3, 'Неплохо, но есть недостатки', 'Квартира хорошая, но шумно от соседей вечером. Вид красивый, но кондиционер работал плохо.', '2025-11-25', 'B-0605', 'neutral', '["noise", "ac", "view"]', true, 'Спасибо за отзыв, Иван! Мы уже заменили кондиционер и поговорили с соседями.', '2025-11-28'),
('booking', 'Sophie Martin', 'France', 2, 'Déçue', 'L appartement était propre mais le bruit de la rue était insupportable. Impossible de dormir.', '2025-11-20', 'A-0301', 'negative', '["noise", "sleep"]', true, 'Nous sommes désolés Sophie. Nous avons ajouté des fenêtres insonorisées. Veuillez nous donner une autre chance!', '2025-11-22');
